### NovaPay API Refinery - Board Certification Tests
# Use With VS Code "REST Client" Extension To Verify All Mission Scenarios

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8088

### 🏦 Scenario 1: Setup Accounts
# Create Employer And Employee Accounts In The Ledger
POST {{baseUrl}}/ledger/account
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "walletId": "8b237fcb-87f1-453c-96ed-0a1e4b068606",
  "currency": "USD"
}

### 🏦 Scenario 2: Setup Employee Account
POST {{baseUrl}}/ledger/account
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "walletId": "665017a0-72b3-49a3-912c-a4e4ab8fb061",
  "currency": "USD"
}

### 🏦 Scenario 3: Create BDT Account (For FX Test)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ledger/account
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "walletId": "665017a0-72b3-49a3-912c-a4e4ab8fb061",
  "currency": "BDT"
}

### 💱 Scenario 4: Get FX Quote (60s TTL)
# @name fxQuote
POST {{baseUrl}}/fx/quote
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromCurrency": "USD",
  "toCurrency": "BDT"
}

### 💸 Scenario 5: Execute International Transfer (FX Single Use)
# Use The ID From The Previous Response To Verify Time-Lock
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions/transfers/international
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromWalletId": "8b237fcb-87f1-453c-96ed-0a1e4b068606",
  "toWalletId": "665017a0-72b3-49a3-912c-a4e4ab8fb061",
  "amount": 1000,
  "currency": "USD",
  "toCurrency": "BDT",
  "quoteId": "{{fxQuote.response.body.id}}",
  "idempotencyKey": "international-test-{{$timestamp}}"
}

### 📑 Scenario 6: Bulk Payroll Job (Idempotent & Serial)
# Verifies Scenario A (Success) And Scenario B (Concurrency)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payroll/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employerId": "hr-manager-novapay",
  "fromWalletId": "8b237fcb-87f1-453c-96ed-0a1e4b068606",
  "items": [
    {
      "userId": "emp-001",
      "walletId": "665017a0-72b3-49a3-912c-a4e4ab8fb061",
      "amount": 5.00,
      "currency": "USD"
    },
    {
      "userId": "emp-002",
      "walletId": "665017a0-72b3-49a3-912c-a4e4ab8fb061",
      "amount": 10.00, 
      "currency": "USD"
    }
  ]
}

### ⚖️ Scenario 7: Atomic Double-Entry Settlement (Manual Audit)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ledger/entry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromWalletId": "8b237fcb-87f1-453c-96ed-0a1e4b068606",
  "toWalletId": "665017a0-72b3-49a3-912c-a4e4ab8fb061",
  "amount": 25.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "transactionId": "manual-audit-{{$timestamp}}"
}

### 📈 Scenario 8: Check Admin Invariant (Security Balance)
# Verifies That No Money Was Created Or Destroyed During Tests
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/ledger-invariant

### 📊 Scenario 9: Business Intelligence Snapshot (Board-Ready Stats)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/business-metrics

### 📊 Scenario 10: Internal Metrics (Prometheus)
GET {{baseUrl}}/metrics
